title: Ashen1shugar's 4th Runescape PK/Staking Video
description:
This is Ashen1shugar&#039;s classic and progressive early &#039;07 Runescape staking/PKing hybrid video. Ashen is a level 102 Runepure with 99 str. This video contains several phat stake wins, and some amazing pk footage as well. Considering the time it was released, it stands as one of the most impressive and progressive staking works ever released, and also had some unprecedented PKing combos (which have since been ruined by piety. :s)

The video is 18 minutes long.

Seeded by Doodlepieguy. You can contact me via PM on the Runevillage forums, under the screen name &#039;Doodle&#039;.
